<v-row>
<v-col :cols='6'>
<vx-datetimepicker v-model='form["ScheduledStartAt"]' v-assign='[form, {"ScheduledStartAt":""}]' :label='"Start at"' :timePickerProps='{"format":"24hr","scrollable":true,"use-seconds":false,"no-title":false}' :clearText='"Clear"' :okText='"OK"'></vx-datetimepicker>

</v-col>
</v-row>
</v-card-text>

<v-spacer></v-spacer>

</v-card-actions>
</v-card>
</v-dialog>
</go-plaid-scope>
"}]}
